headline: CDW Earnings Beat Highlights Cloud And AI Growth Plus Higher Dividend
summary: CDW (NasdaqGS:CDW) reported strong fourth quarter and full year results, with sales and profit performance ahead of earlier expectations. The company highlighted demand for software, cloud, professional services and AI focused solutions as key contributors to the period’s performance. The Board approved a higher quarterly dividend, extending CDW’s pattern of returning cash to shareholders. CDW is an IT solutions provider with exposure to areas many businesses are currently prioritizing,...
